  <scopecontent id="aspace_20c14bbaa8d9f1537063c9039e1ce8fa">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Jamie Whitbeck's collection of ImageOut, the Rochester Lesbian and Gay Film and Video Festival related materials including notes, meeting minutes, correspondence, press releases, festival programs, newsletters, fund raising and promotional materials as well as newspapers and news clippings.</p>  </scopecontent>
